p.k: Gumball saved himself from being trapped in The Void, just in time. The remote has now taken Gumball back to the beginning of that disastrous day. / Fed up with having to listen to Molly's long, tedious anecdotes, Gumball and Darwin try to teach her how to make them sound more exciting. / Gumball and Darwin put Anais' new friend, Josh, through a series of tests, to see if he's good enough for their sister. / Gumball and Darwin are convinced it's a day when nothing interesting is happening. But as they walk around Elmore, it is apparent exciting things are happening just not to them. / Principal Brown tries to “fix” Gumball’s dysfunctional family.
